The code is to search "sydney,nsw" in flickr and save the image title, id, url into the database

It's been developed on
MySQL 5.5 x64
PHP 5.3.8
Phlickr 0.2.7

php curl is required for the application

Note:
Please setup the database in application/config/application.ini and create tables in sql/20120314_init.sql

LIMIT:
No paginating introduced
There is still a PHP Notice from the library Phlickr

Bug:
1. cache still have problem. 
2. proxy setting for curl